X.BG
X.FN qrq
X.TL
XLinearized Quantile Estimation
X.DN
XCompute linearized quantiles from rq data structure.
X.CS
Xqrq(s, a)
X.RA
X.AG s
Xdata structure returned by the quantile regression function rq with t<0 or t>1.
X.AG a
Xthe vector of quantiles for which the corresponding linearized quantiles are to be computed.
X.RT
Xa vector of the linearized quantiles corresponding to vector a,
Xas interpolated from the second row of s$sol.
X.SA SEE ALSO
Xrq and  trq  for further detail.
X.EX
Xz_qrq(rq(x,y),a)       #assigns z the linearized quantiles 
X                       #corresponding to vector a.
X.KW 
X.WR
